learning_outcomes.en:
After cmpleting the course the student knows software tools, including MS Office Project.
After passing the passing the course the student is able to:
* use MS Project program to plan and monitor projects;
* use office software for budgeting, financial management, project and company documents (incl. drawings, tables, etc.);
* use different communication methods (incl. intranet, blog, e-mail) by using different programs.
After passing the course the student knows various virtual communication environments, including Asana, Slack, Skype, Google Docs, etc.
